    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_000&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たち……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You guys...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298824</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;、
おまえ大丈夫か？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey &lt;Dio&gt;, is everything okay?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298896</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、あぁ、うん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y-Yeah, I think I'm okay now, thanks...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298964</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これ……どうぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Here...it's a gift from us.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これは……！
エレメンツポット！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What!? It's an Elements' Pot!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299128</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>中にちゃんと精霊晶核もある！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And it has all of the Atomism
Cores inside already!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299200</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうしたの、こレ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How is this possible!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そいつは&lt;Red&gt;ヴァルハラ&lt;White&gt;の、
『シグルド』のアジトに
残されてた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's one of the things we
found in Sigurd's hideout.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>たぶん……バジル博士が
残したものだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I think... That's one of
Professor Basil's belongings.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299436</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>バジルさんが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mister Basil...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299548</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>中身はオレたちが、
マクスウェルのところで
もらってきたんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We went through the trouble of
going to Maxwell's place and
getting those Core things for you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301132</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>とにかく、
これで『虹輪』ってヤツを
消せるな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So, now you folks can finally
put a stop to the Prism Ring.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301280</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それなんだけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, actually...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301280</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレらが時間を
行き来するのに使ってた
絵が壊されたんだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The paintings we used to travel through
time were destroyed by someone...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301396</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それがないと、
君たちは自分の時代に
戻れないんじゃないのかい？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's a shame. So you guys
can't return to your timeline?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301476</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はい……それで困ってて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes...it's a fine mess...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301564</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>簡単だろ。
&lt;Red&gt;トール&lt;White&gt;を使えばいい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, it's not. We can
just go to &lt;Red&gt;Thor&lt;White&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;超古代都市トール&lt;White&gt;か……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The &lt;Red&gt;Ancient City of Thor&lt;White&gt;, right...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今は安易に使えないよう、
時間転移装置には、見張りが
ついているという話ですよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It shouldn't be too difficult to time travel
from there. We just need to talk to the
main computer guarding the place.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301836</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>行ってみる？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What do you think, &lt;Dio&gt;? Should we go?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301924</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>他に方法ないもんな、
行ってみよう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't see another way. Let's go!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302008</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_060_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それじゃあ、
僕たちで案内しよう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then we'll help you along the way.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
